headline: Gifthealth Celebrates Grand Opening Of New Pharmacy In Mesa

headline: Is It Time To Revisit UPS (NYSE:UPS) After Recent Share Price Weakness
summary: If you are wondering whether United Parcel Service is attractively priced right now, it helps to step back and look at how the market has been treating the stock recently. UPS shares last closed at US$106.97, with returns of 7.8% over 7 days, 10.3% over 30 days, and 5.9% year to date. However, the stock shows a 9.8% decline over 1 year, a 31.9% decline over 3 years, and a 19.6% decline over 5 years.
